Context: The George Brown College offers fully online programs in the academic areas of Business, Computer Technology, and Media & Performing Arts. Students can join live, synchronous classes led by experienced faculty and benefit from the stability and flexibility of an entirely online option. For more information, students can sign up to receive application deadlines, college news, upcoming events, tours, and more. The contact information for the college is 416-415-2000 (voice) and 1-877-515-5559 (TTY), or they can email ask.george@georgebrown.ca. The college's social media hub can also be visited for further information. It is important to note that the information on this website may be subject to change without notice, and students are responsible for verifying George Brown College fee requirements.
